name: Pomplamoose
overview:
Pomplamoose is a California indie duo centered around musicians Jack Conte and Nataly Dawn.

They enjoy making video songs for their recordings, with a few rules:

What you see is what you hear. (No lip-syncing for instruments or voice) If you hear it, at some point you see it. (No hidden sounds) They have also worked with Julia Nunes, Lauren O’Connell, Louis Cole, Louis Cole and Genevieve Artadi, Danielle Ate The Sandwich, Wade Johnston, Ryan Lerman, My Terrible Friend, Ben Folds, Allee Willis, Zoe Keating, Matt Payne, Anton Patzner, Andy Wilke, and Carlos Cabrera. You have heard their music in commercials for Toyota and Hyundai.
